Package: swauth
Architecture: all
Section: net
Depends: python-eventlet (>= 0.17.4),
         swift-proxy (>= 2.2.0),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${python:Depends},
Provides: ${python:Provides},
Description: An alternative authentication system for Swift
 .
 An auth service for Swift as WSGI Middleware that uses Swift itself as a
 backing store. It's alternative to Keystone.
 .
 This package provides the Python libraries that actually implement everything.

Package: swauth-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends: libjs-jquery,
         libjs-underscore,
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: An alternative authentication system for Swift - documentation
 .
 An auth service for Swift as WSGI Middleware that uses Swift itself as a
 backing store. It's alternative to Keystone.
 .
 This package provides the Sphinx generated documentation for Swauth.
